div.p: Thank you for visiting the Wilmot Union High School web page. WUHS has played a significant part in the Western Kenosha County communities for over 110 years. There is a proud tradition of learning and community connection that is woven into the experience of high school every day. From the original seven students in the graduating Class of 1905 to our nearly 300 students expecting to graduate in June, Wilmot has provided a home to a diverse group of learners with a myriad of interests.

p.br: Wilmot Union High School's Mission: As a professional learning community, our core purpose is to ensure our students are college, career, and civic ready by fostering a culture of life-long learning.
